<div id="section4" class="section toc-section"><a id="sec009" name="sec009" class="link-target" title="Outcome of the Rumour Annotation Task"></a><h4>Outcome of the Rumour Annotation Task.</h4><a id="article1.body1.sec2.sec1.sec4.p1" name="article1.body1.sec2.sec1.sec4.p1" class="link-target"></a><p>
<a href="#pone-0150989-t001">Table 1</a> summarises the outcome of the annotation work, showing the number of source tweets annotated as rumours and non-rumours for each of the nine events, as well as the number of rumourous stories, where each story corresponds to a group of rumourous tweets.</p>
